headline.main: Text of U.S. Note to Inter-American Peace Unit Laying 'Provocations' to Cuba

docs.lead_paragraph: FRENCH LICK, Ind., July 1 (AP) -- Mickey Wright of San Diego knocked three strokes off women's par today on the rainsoaked Sheraton County Club course and her 71 led the field of twenty-eight in the opening round of the 72-hole Ladies Professional Golfers Association championship.

headline.main: MISS WRIGHT'S 71 LEADS BY 2 SHOTS; Kathie Whitworth and Mrs. Cornelius Next in First Round of P.G.A. Event

docs.snippet: WASHINGTON, July 1 -- United States patience with the Cuban Government was rubbed thinner today by Havana's seizure of additional foreign-owned property.
